metadata.name: Virtual universe
metadata.description:
Virtual reality is becoming more and more part of our lives. Here it is the Universe that stands before us. Virtuality and reality are intertwined. A new era is coming. But we are still the same people with emotions that cannot be taken away from us ...

We rejoice in flowers, we grieve when we let down the weather, we love the whole world and feel great happiness to be in the moment.

But you can't lag behind the pace, so we are all living here. We run and are afraid to miss something important, forgetting about simple little things.

Smile. Life is beautiful.
